%E1%BA%A7n-Thi%E1%BB%87n-Ch%C3%A1nh/author-bRdZVTN5A-Ykj1jiRsY3BQ">Trần Thiện Chánh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/T%C3%A0n-hoa/poem-N1xrXwX18V3HjIUK1evLgw">Tàn hoa - 殘花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-Trang/author-sRwDvUqTTXJgu1Qk5ewg6w">Vi Trang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem--LsKiQ1eOygSMk7fNhUr8w">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ nhị đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第二段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Li%C3%AAm/Vi%E1%BB%87t-ca/poem-WEJuJvnN-wODOEYeXse6lg">Việt ca - 越歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Li%C3%AAm/author-cJEa_nnPF2Dm3ze1rqMDcA">Tống Liêm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
